{"info": {"author": "Illidan", "author_email": "", "bugtrack_url": null, "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "description": "# NDS Text Generator\nCommand line tool to render text from NDS .NFTR fonts.  \n## Run from pip\n`pip install ndstextgen`  \n`ndstextgen --help`  \n## Run from source\nInstall pipenv.  \n`pipenv install`  \n`pipenv run python ndstextgen --help`  \n## Command line usage\n`ndstextgen <options> FONT \"TEXT\"`  \nExample: `ndstextgen --color red font.NFTR \"Print multiline\\nred text.\"`  \n`FONT`: (Required) Filename of the font, .NFTR extension can be omitted.  \n`TEXT`: (Required) Text to write. \"\\\\n\" can be used for a line break. Can be the name of a UTF-8 file to read the text from.  \n`--out <file>`: Output file, set empty to just return the image. Default: text.png  \n`--vert <int>`: Vertical spacing between lines. Default: 2  \n`--fw <int>`: Use a fixed width instead of the VWF values in the font.  \n`--spacing <int>`: Additional horizontal spacing between characters.  \n`--color <text>`: Color to apply to the font. Default: black  \n`--bg <text>`: Background color. Default: transparent  \n`--width <int>`: Set width for the generated image. Default: 256  \n`--height <int>`: Set height for the generated image. Default: 256  \n`--center`: Center each line.  \n`--wwrap`: Automatic wordwrap.  \n`--no-crop`: Don't crop the image before saving it.  \n## Script usage\n```python\nimport ndstextgen\nimage = ndstextgen.gen(\"font.NFTR\", \"Print multiline\\nred text.\", color=\"red\")\n```\n\n\n", "description_content_type": "text/markdown", "docs_url": null, "download_url": "", "downloads": {"last_day": -1, "last_month": -1, "last_week": -1}, "home_page": "https://github.com/Illidanz/ndstextgen", "keywords": "", "license": "", "maintainer": "", "maintainer_email": "", "name": "ndstextgen", "package_url": "https://pypi.org/project/ndstextgen/", "platform": "", "project_url": "https://pypi.org/project/ndstextgen/", "project_urls": {"Homepage": "https://github.com/Illidanz/ndstextgen"}, "release_url": "https://pypi.org/project/ndstextgen/1.5.0/", "requires_dist": ["hacktools (>=0.11)"], "requires_python": ">=3.7", "summary": "Command line tool to render text from NDS .NFTR fonts.", "version": "1.5.0", "yanked": false, "html_description": "<div class=\"project-description\">\n            <h1>NDS Text Generator</h1>\n<p>Command line tool to render text from NDS .NFTR fonts.</p>\n<h2>Run from pip</h2>\n<p><code>pip install ndstextgen</code><br>\n<code>ndstextgen --help</code></p>\n<h2>Run from source</h2>\n<p>Install pipenv.<br>\n<code>pipenv install</code><br>\n<code>pipenv run python ndstextgen --help</code></p>\n<h2>Command line usage</h2>\n<p><code>ndstextgen &lt;options&gt; FONT \"TEXT\"</code><br>\nExample: <code>ndstextgen --color red font.NFTR \"Print multiline\\nred text.\"</code><br>\n<code>FONT</code>: (Required) Filename of the font, .NFTR extension can be omitted.<br>\n<code>TEXT</code>: (Required) Text to write. \"\\n\" can be used for a line break. Can be the name of a UTF-8 file to read the text from.<br>\n<code>--out &lt;file&gt;</code>: Output file, set empty to just return the image. Default: text.png<br>\n<code>--vert &lt;int&gt;</code>: Vertical spacing between lines. Default: 2<br>\n<code>--fw &lt;int&gt;</code>: Use a fixed width instead of the VWF values in the font.<br>\n<code>--spacing &lt;int&gt;</code>: Additional horizontal spacing between characters.<br>\n<code>--color &lt;text&gt;</code>: Color to apply to the font. Default: black<br>\n<code>--bg &lt;text&gt;</code>: Background color. Default: transparent<br>\n<code>--width &lt;int&gt;</code>: Set width for the generated image. Default: 256<br>\n<code>--height &lt;int&gt;</code>: Set height for the generated image. Default: 256<br>\n<code>--center</code>: Center each line.<br>\n<code>--wwrap</code>: Automatic wordwrap.<br>\n<code>--no-crop</code>: Don't crop the image before saving it.</p>\n<h2>Script usage</h2>\n<pre><span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"nn\">ndstextgen</span>\n<span class=\"n\">image</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">ndstextgen</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">gen</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"font.NFTR\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"Print multiline</span><span class=\"se\">\\n</span><span class=\"s2\">red text.\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">color</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">\"red\"</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</pre>\n\n          </div>"}, "last_serial": 7186318, "releases": {"1.0.0": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "215aa965d362f68d72c50ab7c47efacb", "sha256": "33e0bc4d8c3bf9e951397ee8b05e3819e768945b6e2c9f3a4d52ebf146a4ac38"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "ndstextgen-1.0.0-py3-none-any.whl", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "215aa965d362f68d72c50ab7c47efacb", "packagetype": "bdist_wheel", "python_version": "py3", "requires_python": ">=3.7", "size": 4121, "upload_time": "2020-04-23T15:35:09", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2020-04-23T15:35:09.871383Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/f8/a3/a1ddac39605c7bdc1b5cfcefb3554aa25136c5f37651b525ad4875f505ee/ndstextgen-1.0.0-py3-none-any.whl", "yanked": false}, {"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "b423980fd8cde52d378634fd2ee4f5f4", "sha256": "be7f8a889aa2ea349b5de4db6e116e266f8adc94c1f9ebc69fa73c3d3fa9bbe8"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "ndstextgen-1.0.0.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "b423980fd8cde52d378634fd2ee4f5f4", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": ">=3.7", "size": 2713, "upload_time": "2020-04-23T15:35:11", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2020-04-23T15:35:11.831928Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/fc/1c/6120ceab9c54445b5d5c0b0d65c41047f53f2591327c7c9f5a6929154576/ndstextgen-1.0.0.tar.gz", "yanked": false}]